messages.text: You sure you don’t wanna come with me to pick out baby clothes? :)
Can’t. Gotta help my mom with something
And I just think it’d be good for us to do this together :)
But what? I’m waiting for the but
I don’t think she’d want to
She’s not too excited that we got pregnant right before graduation
It’s not that big of a deal
She doesn’t seem to think so
Almost there. Get me a latte ;)
(pause to type) You. Who else would it be?
It’s an old text to my mom
What are you helping her with again?
(pause to type) She needs help hanging a picture
She also needs help with other stuff. It’s just her you know
What other stuff does she need help with???
We can go together with your mom
That way I can ask her about what you helped her with
I mean it’s stupid to ask because it’s easy to answer
That’s what I wanted to hear
You know it won’t be so bad when he’s born
Especially since we’re both going to State
That’s funny because I just drove by the one by the mall
And I swear I saw your car parked out front
I’m at my mom’s so it can’t be me
(pause to type) I love you too :)
You know what, I might turn around and get a latte
I have a taste for one for some reason
Don’t play dumb. I’m parked at the mall
I see you with some blonde girl who’s getting on a bike!!!!
You like her because she’s fit???!!!
She’s pretty fast on her bike though
But I’m sure I can catch her
You should wanna be with me!!! Not stop me!!
That’s why I wanna stop you
She can’t live too far away
Once this light turns I’ll see where she went
We were talking about the baby
Her parents are rich too, huh?
Does she go to that prep school?
She should’ve put on her helmet
Too bad I got these texts for evidence for the cops
Too bad you’ll have to raise the baby yourself if I’m in prison
